<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Low Inventory Alert</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .alert {
      background-color: #ffecb3;
      border-left: 4px solid #FF9800;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .alert-title {
      color: #FF6F00;
      margin-top: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Low Inventory Alert</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{vendorName}},</p>
      
      <div class="alert">
        <h3 class="alert-title">⚠️ Low Stock Alert</h3>
        <p>One of your products has reached low inventory levels and may need restocking soon.</p>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Product Details:</h2>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <td>{{productName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Product ID</th>
          <td>{{productId}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Current Stock</th>
          <td><strong>{{currentStock}} units</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Low Stock Threshold</th>
          <td>{{threshold}} units</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      
      <p>We recommend restocking this product soon to avoid running out of inventory and potentially missing sales.</p>
      
      <p>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Update Inventory</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>Thank you for being a valued vendor on our platform.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>Yunike Marketplace Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
      <p>© {{currentYear}} Yunike Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 